This package contains the Python and Javascript sources for Socialcalc for the OLPC XO laptop.

You can download the latest built package from this URL:

  http://github.com/lukec/socialcalc-xocom/raw/master/dist/SocialCalcActivity-1.xo

The project homepage is:

  https://www.socialtext.net/lukec/?socialcalc_xocom


Instructions to install it on your OLPC:

* Open the terminal, we will delete the old package (if it is there)
> rm -rf ~/Activities/SocialCalcActivity.activity

* Restart Sugar (only necessary if you deleted the old package)
** Hit Ctrl, Alt, Backspace

* Open the terminal again
> wget http://is.gd/fqnd -O socialcalc.xo
> sugar-install-bundle socialcalc.xo

* It should appear on your OLPC home page now

